      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 14:26:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国与中国争论谁对其产业补贴最多</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/us-spars-with-china-over-who-subsidizes-its-industries-the-most</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国和中国周五在世界贸易组织 (WTO) 就工业补贴问题发生争执，北京要求成立争端小组，审查《通胀削减法案》的税收抵免，而华盛顿则指责中国虚伪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/us-spars-with-china-over-who-subsidizes-its-industries-the-most</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 14:14:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚财政部长否认在贪污丑闻中存在不当行为</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/colombia-finance-chief-denies-wrongdoing-in-embezzlement-scandal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚财政部长里卡多·博尼利亚否认有任何不当行为，并表示在检察官提及他涉嫌贪污调查后，他不会辞职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/colombia-finance-chief-denies-wrongdoing-in-embezzlement-scandal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 14:07:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>古巴急需美元，禁止美国银行开展业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/desperate-for-dollars-cuba-bars-businesses-from-us-banks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[古巴正禁止其新兴企业家阶层使用美国银行账户，以便在该国遭遇苏联解体以来最严重的经济危机之际将美元留在国内。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/desperate-for-dollars-cuba-bars-businesses-from-us-banks</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 13:34:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芬兰称俄罗斯船只闯入其海域侵犯其领土</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/finland-says-russia-ship-sailed-into-its-waters-in-territorial-breach</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芬兰称，一艘俄罗斯船只涉嫌侵犯芬兰湾东部领土，这是莫斯科一系列侵犯边界行为中的最新一次。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/finland-says-russia-ship-sailed-into-its-waters-in-territorial-breach</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 13:27:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴黎铁路破坏事件后仍坚持奥运会开幕式计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/sabotage-acts-disrupt-train-traffic-in-france-minister-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴黎超高速铁路网络遭遇“大规模袭击”，列车运行中断，给 2024 年奥运会开幕式蒙上阴影。巴黎仍计划继续举办开幕式。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/sabotage-acts-disrupt-train-traffic-in-france-minister-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 06:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
